#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In these modules, you can configure various aspects of &konqueror;'s file "
#| "manager functionality."
msgid ""
"In these modules, you can configure various aspects of &konqueror;’s file "
"manager functionality."
msgstr ""
"इन मॉड्यूल में, आप &konqueror; की फ़ाइल प्रबंधक कार्यक्षमता के विभिन्न पहलुओं को कॉन्फ़िगर "
"कर सकते हैं।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&konqueror;'s web browser functionality has its <ulink url=\"help:/"
#| "kcontrol/khtml-behavior/index.html\">own configuration modules</ulink>."
msgid ""
"&konqueror;’s web browser functionality has its <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"khtml-behavior/index.html\">own configuration modules</ulink>."
msgstr "&konqueror; की वेब ब्राउज़र कार्यक्षमता के अपने स्वयं के कॉन्फ़िगरेशन मॉड्यूल हैं।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Options"
msgstr "विविध विकल्प"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "फ़ोल्डरों को अलग-अलग विंडो में खोलें"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when "
#| "you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in "
#| "the current window."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"यदि यह विकल्प चुना गया है, तो जब आप कोई फ़ोल्डर खोलेंगे तो एक नई &konqueror; विंडो "
"बनाई जाएगी, बजाय इसके कि उस फ़ोल्डर की सामग्री वर्तमान विंडो में दिखाई दे।"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Show 'Delete' menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr "'हटाएँ' मेनू प्रविष्टियाँ दिखाएँ जो कूड़ेदान को बायपास करती हैं"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be "
#| "displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can "
#| "always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling "
#| "<guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"यदि आप चाहते हैं कि <quote>Delete</quote> मेनू कमांड डेस्कटॉप पर और फ़ाइल मैनेजर के संदर्भ "
"मेनू में प्रदर्शित हों, तो इसे चेक करें। आप <guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem> को "
"कॉल करते समय &Shift; कुंजी दबाकर फ़ाइलों को हमेशा हटा सकते हैं।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &konqueror;'s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
#| "Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> "
#| "pages are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgid ""
"The settings for &konqueror;’s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
"Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> pages "
"are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>दृश्य मोड</guilabel>, <guilabel>नेविगेशन</guilabel>, <guilabel>सेवाएं</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>सामान्य</guilabel> और <guilabel>ट्रैश</guilabel> पृष्ठों पर "
"&konqueror; के फ़ाइल प्रबंधक मोड के लिए सेटिंग्स का उपयोग &dolphin; द्वारा भी किया "
"जाता है।"
